code: public static GenericContainer natsContainer() {     return new GenericContainer(CONTAINER_IMAGE).withNetworkAliases(CONTAINER_NAME).waitingFor(Wait.forLogMessageContaining("Server is ready", 1)).withCommand("-DV", "-auth", TOKEN). }
public String getNatsUrl() {     return String.format("%s@%s:%d", TOKEN, getContainerHost(CONTAINER_NAME), getContainerPort(CONTAINER_NAME, 4222)). }
